      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, complete with individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. The dual-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a known structural point\u2014has been professionally reinforced for enhanced torsional rigidity. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The suspension kinematics remain taut, and the engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders. This is a mechanically pristine, turn-key example for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
